column4: T. Rowe Price nearly halves stake in Tesla to 5.2 percent:  filing
column5: Tesla Inc shareholder T. Rowe Price Group Inc had a 5.2 percent stake in the electric car maker as of end-December  roughly half its earlier stake  a regulatory filing https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/80255/000008025519001855/tsla13gadec18.htm showed on Monday.
